Back Office Operation - Medan Branch
Responsibilities
Responsible for transaction of intra city clearing, internal account (non-financial categories account), and other accounts handling, city clearing in BI system (SKN), establishment book keeping for daily intra-city clearing registration.Responsible for squaring transaction, checking cash balance, checking all the approved transaction voucher.  Requirements: Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree, Finance/Accountancy/Banking, Business Studies/Administration/Management, Others, Commerce or equivalent.Required language: English and ChineseAt least 2 years of working experience in the related field is required for this position.
